    <who name="Brian Bauman">baumanbr</who>
    <bug_when>2008-01-09 13:15:28 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>Changed the preference for indenting line comments in the first column.  Now when you use ctrl + /, the line should not be indented.  If we find this causes problems, we might change it back later.</thetext>
